  "id": "1",
  "name": "Laptop",
  "price": 1000,
  "quantity": 1
}
```

If added again:

```json
{
  "id": "1",
  "name": "Laptop",
  "price": 1000,
  "quantity": 2
}
```

It becomes:

```
Quantity = 3 (merged, not duplicated)
```

